{
  "stem": "18102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 49.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the curriculum was complete until you were moved onto the next grade, and then you got another teacher that had its curriculum for the following grade.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My mother had the younger grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she would have first grade, second grade, and third grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were her classes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, on the other hand, who was a mathematician whose books were used throughout Poland, Yiddish schools-- the math books that he wrote for grade school students eight nine, eighth and ninth grade, seventh, eighth, and ninth grades, were used throughout Poland in Yiddish schools.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he, of course, taught-- taught the older grades which included the higher grade math.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, again, when you were in seventh or eighth grade, your teacher did it all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whether it was biology or whether it was history or-- or literature or math, it was that teacher that gave it all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't go from classroom to classroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I recall, that's how those classes worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The school they taught in was called [INAUDIBLE], named after its founder, someone named Grosse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know his first name at this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, my father graduated from the Leipzig Institute as I recall now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he, too, had very high grades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember seeing his [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they taught in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, of course, it was-- it was a grammar school that began late August, as I recall, and lasted through June.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a long-- a long good teaching year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Much to my disappointment, I thought that by-- by virtue of the fact that my parents were teachers, I would be in my mother's classroom.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was disappointed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
